text: Patrick Testin (born June 9, 1988) is a Wisconsin politician and legislator. Born in Madison, Wisconsin, Testin received his bachelor's degree in political science from the University of Wisconsin-Stevens Point. Testin lived in Stevens Point, Wisconsin.
